ttfautohint|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
ttfautohint: ttfautohint (Automated hinting utility for TrueType fonts)
ttfautohint:
ttfautohint: This is a utility which takes a TrueType font as the input, removes
ttfautohint: its bytecode instructions (if any), and returns a new font where all
ttfautohint: glyphs are bytecode hinted using the information given by FreeType's
ttfautohint: autohinting module. The idea is to provide the excellent quality of
ttfautohint: the autohinter on platforms which don't use FreeType.
ttfautohint:
ttfautohint: http://www.freetype.org/ttfautohint
ttfautohint:
ttfautohint: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
